/*

Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
20 March 2018	jlgndl1	Initial creation	TFS 37550

*/

vars

begin
	if self.auditId() &lt;&gt; null then
		return app.getErrorString(Currency_type) &amp; " - " &amp; self.auditId();
